Sep 9 2007 	loved the ocean park motel	We just stayed one night at the ocean park before flying back but we really liked it. The guy at the reception was super friendly and provided us with lots of useful information ( map, history of the motel and recommendations for restaurants etc ).The Art Deco style of the motel is great, the courtyard fantastic. The room was nicely decorated and very clean.The location 2 streets off the beach and the zoo is not very central but you have easy access to public transport which gets you downtown in about 30 mins. If you come by car there is free parking. Very safe area and you can hear the ocean from your room.The motel does not provide breakfast but there are a few cafés and a deli in walking distance.	
